<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
  Curated showcase records for the BibframeHub demo.

  Each record carries its VERIFIED canonical LC Hub URI in 240 $1 (the Modern
  MARC "fast lane"), so the plugin resolves deterministically and the
  surprise-scoring model has a richly-connected base-work hub to traverse.

  Hubs were chosen by querying the neo4j-hubs-v2 graph (2026-05-05 LC dump) for
  bidirectional relation degree, then confirming authorship via id.loc.gov RDF.
  The set is deliberately weighted toward diverse and international voices.
  See heng-et-al-2026/find_richest_hubs.py and /memories/session/showcase-hubs.md.
-->
